INFO.name: QUERY
INFO.value: SELECT * FROM ivoa.ObsCore WHERE dataproduct_type IN ( 'image', 'cube' ) AND (INTERSECTS(CIRCLE('ICRS',20.0,30.0,0.2), s_region) = 1)

FIELD.name: obs_collection
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: short name for the data colection

FIELD.name: obs_release_date
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: timestamp of date the data becomes publicly available

FIELD.name: s_fov
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: size of the region covered (~diameter of minimum bounding circle)

FIELD.name: s_xel1
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: dimensions (number of pixels) along one spatial axis

FIELD.name: s_xel2
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: dimensions (number of pixels) along the other spatial axis

FIELD.name: t_xel
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: dimensions (number of pixels) along the time axis

FIELD.name: em_xel
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: dimensions (number of pixels) along the energy axis

FIELD.name: pol_states
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: polarization states present in the data

FIELD.name: pol_xel
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: dimensions (number of pixels) along the polarization axis

FIELD.name: o_ucd
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: UCD describing the observable axis (pixel values)

FIELD.name: lastModified
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: timestamp of last modification of the metadata
